003package es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step.tpptokenization;
004
005import java.util.Set;
006
007import es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.abstracttppstep.AbstractTppProcessingStepService;
008import es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.entity.ProcessedDocument;
009import es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step.AbstractProcessingStep;
010import es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step.tpptokenization.entity.TppTokenizedTextDocument;
011import es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step.tpptokenization.entity.TppTokenizedTextWithTitleDocument;
012import es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step.xml.definition.AbstractProcessingStepParameter;
013
014/**
015 * The service implementation for this processing step.
016 *
017 * @author Alejandro González García
018 */
019public final class TppTokenizationProcessingStepService extends AbstractTppProcessingStepService {
020        @Override
021        public AbstractProcessingStep create() {
022                return new TppTokenizationProcessingStep();
023        }
024
025        @Override
026        public String getName() {
027                return "TppTokenization";
028        }
029
030        @Override
031        public Set<Class<? extends ProcessedDocument>> getProcessedDocumentTypes() {
032                return Set.of(TppTokenizedTextDocument.class, TppTokenizedTextWithTitleDocument.class);
033        }
034
035        @Override
036        protected Set<Class<? extends AbstractProcessingStepParameter>> getAdditionalParticularParameters() {
037                return Set.of();
038        }
039}
